      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"5. REGAL GYPSY continues to build a strong record and was impressive winner in quick time last start when scoring by 1.75 lengths (25.38) at this track. Is yet to taste defeat at this distance. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Hard to fault the current string of winning form and can continue her winning ways. 1. DRINK MOJITOS did a good job to finish third last time out over 390m at this track (22.11) in a Grade 5, the second top-three finish on the trot. Rates a winning chance on best. 2. RAPTOR GIRL was checked and settled off speed but recovered to turn in front, lifting to a neck win (23.93) at Rockhampton in a Grade 5. Has the ability and looks a key chance. 8. GIGLIO is a last start winner and can go on with it.\",\"runners\":[5,1,2,8],\"exclusive\":false}",
